data.description: Gorgeous Two Story, 4 Bedroom, 3.5 Bath situated  in Cypresswood Point Subdivision. Beautiful Laminated wood flooring on first floor and upstairs is carpet. The Home Features High Ceiling Foyer. Family Room with Fireplace Open to the kitchen, Formal Living and Dining, Breakfast Rm. Primary Bedroom down. Kitchen has a kitchen Island  and 42” Cabinetry. The second Floor has an expansive Game Room, 3 large Bedrooms, . You will love the updates, including New Laminated Wood Flooring and Fresh Paint in 2023.  Community Amenities include a Park, Swimming Pool, and Playground. Home Conveniently located with easy access to Deerbrook Mall, Cypresswood Golf Club, and JAH Airport. I-45, I-59, Hardy Toll Road. You don't want to miss all this gorgeous home has to offer!
